snippet.title: CATAN - Console Edition Announce Trailer | Coming 2023!
snippet.description: CATAN® – Console Edition, coming 2023, Wishlist today! Play the official video game of CATAN on Console. Acquire resources, master new strategies, and build your settlements across a board that comes to life. Challenge friends both online and in the living room or play against smart & dynamic AI to become the winning Catanian!
